      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Affordable and honest transportation with plenty of potential. This vehicle is best suited for a buyer looking for a budget-friendly daily driver, a starter car, or a project opportunity. It offers solid value for the money and a chance to get on the road without a major investment. Priced to sell, this is a practical option for someone who sees the upside in a straightforward used vehicle.",
