      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for a cheap set of wheels with plenty of life left for the right person? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest budget-friendly option that could make a great starter, backup car, or little project for someone handy. It\u2019s priced to reflect its condition and gives you a chance to get on the road without spending a fortune. If you want something affordable and straightforward, come have a look.",
